    <item>
      <title>以色列扩大对黎巴嫩的打击范围，考虑对伊朗进行报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/israel-widens-strikes-on-hezbollah-as-it-weighs-iran-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列周六扩大了对黎巴嫩真主党目标的袭击，以色列政府正在权衡如何报复伊朗本周早些时候的导弹袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/israel-widens-strikes-on-hezbollah-as-it-weighs-iran-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 17:28:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一名幼儿和另外三人在试图横渡英吉利海峡时死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-05/attempts-to-cross-the-english-channel-on-small-boats-leave-4-migrants-including-a-child-dead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴黎（美联社）——法国当局称，周六，四名移民（其中包括一名 2 岁儿童）在试图穿越英吉利海峡前往英国时在两起独立事件中死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-05/attempts-to-cross-the-english-channel-on-small-boats-leave-4-migrants-including-a-child-dead</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 16:49:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>出口民调预测莫迪的对手将在邦选举中获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/exit-polls-predict-win-for-modi-s-opponents-in-state-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[出口民调显示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党在最近两次邦选举中落后，由于执政联盟在全国选举中的支持率较弱，这给反对党提供了助力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/exit-polls-predict-win-for-modi-s-opponents-in-state-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 16:02:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔承诺在评级下调后迅速采取行动弥补预算缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/senegal-pledges-swift-action-on-budget-gap-after-ratings-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔表示，将迅速采取行动降低预算赤字。审计显示该国财政和债务状况较弱，导致穆迪评级下调了该国的评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/senegal-pledges-swift-action-on-budget-gap-after-ratings-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 15:26:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
