    <item>
      <title>英国财政部长里夫斯审查终止私募股权税收减免的办法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/uk-s-reeves-reviews-approach-to-closing-private-equity-tax-break</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 仍打算取消私募股权的税收减免，但正在重新审视其方法，以最大限度地增加税收收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/uk-s-reeves-reviews-approach-to-closing-private-equity-tax-break</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 12:52:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩，袭击贝鲁特郊区和北部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-05/israel-strikes-lebanon-hitting-beirut-suburbs-and-the-north</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩马斯纳边境口岸 (美联社) — 以色列周六扩大了对黎巴嫩的轰炸，对贝鲁特南部郊区进行了十几次空袭，并首次袭击了北部深处的一个巴勒斯坦难民营，轰炸目标同时是真主党和哈马斯战士。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-05/israel-strikes-lebanon-hitting-beirut-suburbs-and-the-north</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 11:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
